Project Overview – Microsoft Excel (Sales Data Analysis)

As a PGDM Big Data Analytics student, this project serves as a demonstration of my proficiency in Microsoft Excel through hands-on data analysis of a basic sales dataset.

Key Tasks Performed:

✔ Structured the dataset by inserting a dynamic Excel Table for better data management.

✔ Applied Sorting and Filtering to enable quick access to relevant information.

✔ Utilized IF conditions for logical data segmentation and mining.

✔ Implemented VLOOKUP for efficient data referencing across the sheet.

✔ Created a Pivot Table to build a data model and perform in-depth sales analysis.

This project highlights my ability to transform raw data into actionable insights using core Excel functionalities.


